verbose_text: Interestingly, however, water permeability of oocytes expressing draqp3a and -3 b was reduced by acidic pH, as found for mammalian AQP3 [XREF_BIBR] and European eel (Anguilla anguilla) Aqp3 [XREF_BIBR], with maximum permeability occurring at pH 8.5.
evidence: water permeability of oocytes expressing draqp3a and -3b was reduced by acidic pH
